data.description: This property screams investment and its priced to sell.  A brand new u-shaped driveway was recently poured.    Making it easier to get in and out, adds extra parking and allows cemented access to the side of the home.  Carport allows shaded parking during the hottest times of the day.  Fenced in backyard.  Walking distance to Smith's Grocery Store and Havasu's Main Street night life.  Easy, quick access anywhere to town.  With some updating and some love, this could be a great investment opportunity.
